 a site that is more line in your business brand. Read more in the <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/docs/checathlon-plus-features/\">Checathlon Plus documentation</a>.</p>\n<h2>Custom Fonts</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-13608\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Checathlon fonts in the Customizer\" width=\"740\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-1024x576.png 1024w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-300x169.png 300w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-768x432.png 768w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-1240x698.png 1240w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts-1080x608.png 1080w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-fonts.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In the Customizer under <strong>Theme Fonts</strong> you can change fonts for</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Site title</li>\n<li>Post title</li>\n<li>Main navigation links</li>\n<li>Headings</li>\n<li>Base body font for text</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Fonts include over twenty Google fonts, system fonts, and web safe fonts. I haven&#8217;t included all available <a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/\">Google fonts</a> but I&#8217;ll add fonts that I think fits for the theme.</p>\n<p>Only the fonts that are not default fonts in the Checathlon theme are used in the front end of your site. This ensures that your site remain fast.</p>\n<h2>Custom Colors</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-colors.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-13624\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Checathlon-colors-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Change theme colors in the Customizer\" width=\"740\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https://foxland.f