foxnet.fi/downloads/category/themes/\">themes</a> are now 75 euros. This is not a big change when the cheapest option was normally 69 euros before. There are several great free themes also without Pro version or additional featured plugin.</p>\n<h2>Free Plugins</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/downloads/edd-members/\">EDD Members</a> and <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/downloads/paytrail-payment-gateway/\">EDD Paytrail payment gateway</a>plugins are now free. I might eventually put them in <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/\">WordPress.org</a>. For current customers I provide support as always.</p>\n<p>I no longer maintain <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/downloads/edd-feedback/\">EDD Feedback</a> plugin. There are so many better ways to automate feedback emails than EDD Feedback.</p>\n<p>Let me know if you have any questions.</p>\n","<p>Today is December 6, 2016, Finland Independence day. We are now 99 years old and I salute my home country from the bottom of my heart. Feature image (dark road with arrow up) represent December here in Finland pretty well, at least here in Helsinki  But what were the changes in my theme and [&hellip;]</p>\n",["4172"],["4173"],["4174"],["4175"],["4176"],["4177"],["4178"],["4179"],["4180","4181"],["4182"],"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/?p=14092","2016 Guest Posts in WP Tavern","<p>In 2016 I wrote two guest post in <a href=\"https://wptavern.com/\">WP Tavern</a>.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://wptavern.com/behind-the-scenes-of-wordpress-com-themes-with-david-kennedy\">Behind the Scenes of WordPress.com Themes with David Kennedy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wptavern.com/why-pixelgrade-is-experimenting-with-a-225-wordpress-theme-on-themeforest\">Why PixelGrade is Experimenting with a $225 WordPress Theme on Themeforest</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>In David&#8217;s interview we talked aboutthemes on WordPress.com, Twenty Seventeen, theme user experience, accessibility, theme business, and other theme-related topics. This 