o ahead, break it!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Is there something else you would like to see?Let me know in the comments if you have other ideas.</p>\n","<p>WordPress Theme review processes can vary a lot. I&#8217;ll try to summarize what kind of reviews I&#8217;d like to see and then write about my experiences about theme reviews in different places. Stay tuned for at least these ones: ThemeReview.cotheme review by Justin Tadlock and Sakin Shrestha. WordPress.org theme review. WordPress.com theme review. Theme Forest [&hellip;]</p>\n",["4611"],["4612"],["4613"],["4614"],["4615"],["4616"],["4617"],["4618"],["4619","4620"],["4621"],"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/?p=4606","Munsa: WordPress Theme for creative people","<p>It&#8217;s releaseday for <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/downloads/munsa/\">Munsa Theme</a>and it feels good!Munsa is a minimal WordPress Theme for creative people like photobloggers, artists and brokerage sites. It has a clean and fresh responsive design. Check out the <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/\">demo for better view</a>.<a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4482\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Munsa_laptop-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"Munsa_laptop\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Munsa_laptop-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Munsa_laptop-300x225.jpg 300w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Munsa_laptop-768x576.jpg 768w, https://foxland.foxnet.fi/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Munsa_laptop.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<p>I&#8217;ll try to keep my themes simple so that you can just install and start using them. I have a interesting background story why this theme turned out like this but I don&#8217;t have permission to tell that quite yet.</p>\n<p>Anyways I really like this black and white, clean and creativeapproach. It&#8217;s kind of a Pro version of my <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/downloads/simppeli/\">Simppeli</a> theme.</p>\n<p>There are couple of Page Templates in this theme which you can manage from the Customizer. Demo site have good info about these features.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/\">Front Page</a> template where you can show featured pages, blog posts and contact info. Featured pages and contact info comes from the Customizer. Featured image fills the full screen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/get-in-touch/\">Contact Info</a> template where you can show contact info and it&#8217;s child pages. This is great fit for showcasing your team members.\n<ul>\n<li>You can set Contact info in the Customizer and there is also customwidget for showing your contact info.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/child-pages/\">Child Page</a> template for showing just it&#8217;s child pages.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/coming-soon/\">Full Background Image</a> template where featured image fills the full screen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/featured-image-on-the-right/\">Featured Image on the Right</a> or <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/featured-image-on-the-left/\">left</a>.</li>\n<li>Definitely check out <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/blog/\">blog</a> page also.</li>\n<li>Munsa have also couple of fancy <a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/child-pages/styling/\">styling elements</a>:\n<ul>\n<li>Videos are automatically a little bit wider than the content when there is enough room.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://foxland.foxnet.fi/demo/munsa/audio-twin/\">Audio</a>just looks better than default.</li>\n<li>Enter image class called <code>wide</code> and center align or no align image will get wider than content. Image needs to be wider than 720 pixels.</li>\n<li>You can highli